  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564920/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1765184226\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564920/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1765184226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564920/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1765184226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Features of the game: <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dark Forest <br></li><li>Laser Sight<br></li><li>Endless rounds of ammunition <br></li><li>Dangerous plants <br></li><li>Teleports-TV sets <br></li><li>Achievements<br></li><li>Complex saws and doors </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564920/extras/284a10738a165290a318e86878d47c90.avif?t=1765184226\" width=610 height=308 /></span><br> <br>Features of conducting a firefight: <br>You can fire standing, sitting, and jumping! A bullet fired by the main character can stop the enemy's bullet. <br>If you are being shot at, you can crouch or jump. <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564920/extras/e5b82e6b462a21a13625e1bf5e3fef67.poster.avif?t=1765184226\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564920/extras/e5b82e6b462a21a13625e1bf5e3fef67.webm?t=1765184226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564920/extras/e5b82e6b462a21a13625e1bf5e3fef67.mp4?t=1765184226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>History: <br>The main character is a former military man sent to investigate in a dark forest, where a lot of strange things happen.",
